    <p>
        GCE TN Chapter Trust was established in Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India, on 24th July 2015 by a group of 5 old students of Ghousia College of Engineering,
        Ramanagaram, Karnataka, India, to support the economically underprivileged old students of Ghousia College of Engineering and other people,
        who live in / hail from Tamil Nadu, The Trust was founded by Mohamed Riyal from 88 Batch and ably supported by Mr. Vasan 84 batch,
        Mr. Charles Vijaykumar 85 batch, Mr. Abdul Rahim 87 batch and Mr. Syed Mehboob Basha 88 batch in setting up this Trust.
    </p>

