                <p>
                    Our mission is to support the needy financially, in Job or career search , family counselling, etc.,
                    The mission can be achieved by creating or developing entrepreneurs amongst us, by providing technical
                    support or provide expert advice to those who require to run or develop their own business,
                    with the help of our GCE friends who have expertise in that field. To provide secondary source of income
                    by creating partnership between mutually interested and agreeable friends to join their existing business
